                        <ab type="script" part="N">Hand a: Rather fine. Hand b: Mediocre, but careful.</ab>
                        <seg type="ink" part="N">Black, red (brown: fols. 2r-8v, vivid scarlet: fols. 10r-15v; strong red: 16r-74v, 89r-90v; vermillion/brown: fols. 76r-89r, 91r</seg>
